## SF5-102 — Multi-Selection Law ✅

**22/22 tests passing** (9 original + 13 new)

### Files created/modified:

1. **`packages/domain/src/selection.ts`** *(new)* — Defines three domain types:
   - `SelectionMode`: `'replace' | 'add' | 'toggle'`
   - `SelectionRect`: `{ x, y, width, height }` for marquee selection
   - `SelectionBounds`: `{ minX, minY, maxX, maxY }` computed union bounds

2. **`packages/state/src/selectionStore.ts`** *(modified)* — Extended with 5 new actions while keeping all 5 original actions backward-compatible:
   - `selectWithMode(itemId, mode)` — replace/add/toggle semantics
   - `selectByRect(rect, items)` — AABB overlap test for marquee selection
   - `getSelectionBounds()` — union bounding box from documentStore (returns null if nothing selected)
   - `selectAll(layerId)` — select every item on a layer
   - `invertSelection(layerId)` — toggle all items on a layer (preserves selections on other layers)

3. **`packages/state/src/__tests__/selectionStore.test.ts`** *(modified)* — Added 13 new tests covering all new APIs and explicit backward-compat checks.